The paper also discusses traditional machine learning algorithms, which fall under the categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also discusses computer vision tasks, which fall under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper discusses ensemble methods, which fall under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, and cs.DS, in that order.
